      <Placemark>
        <name>Northwest</name>
        <description>The Atlanta Beltline Northwest Trail will run 4.3 miles from the northern terminus of the Atlanta Beltline Westside Trail (in the area of West Marietta and Huff Road) over to the Atlanta Beltline Northeast Trail (in the area of the Armour-Ottley commercial district and the Lindbergh MARTA station).</description>
